{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rust &amp; Roots</strong> is a mission-based, isometric top-down shooter that plunges you into chaos. As the last surviving warriors of hope in a devastated world, fight to save the future of humanity from the clutches of a mechanised catastrophe. In this bleak universe, danger never ends, even as night falls.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What the game offers:</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mission Based Open World: Complete immersive missions in a semi-open world and explore deeper through side stories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dark and Realistic Atmosphere: A night world filled with wastelands, abandoned cities, and landscapes destroyed by technology.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemy Diversity: Face hordes of robots and massive mechanical war machines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategic Gameplay: Use the environment to your advantage to defeat your enemies, save your bullets and enter the battlefield with the right equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intense Action: Engage in tactical skirmishes with twin stick controls that test your quick reflexes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445360/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737715529","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445360/page.bg.jpg?t=1737715529","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445360/2827ea1419562a40d28898d4a099d220866d0699/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737715529","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445360/2827ea1419562a40d28898d4a099d220866d0699/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737715529","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":